2
00:00:11,290 --> 00:00:12,860
Where do you want to go?

3
00:00:12,860 --> 00:00:15,160
I want to eat something good.

4
00:00:13,100 --> 00:00:15,160
You're so bad.

5
00:00:15,160 --> 00:00:16,950
One more! One more!

6
00:00:19,620 --> 00:00:21,390
Hey, isn't this cute?

7
00:00:21,390 --> 00:00:23,160
Yeah, it's so cute.

8
00:00:35,190 --> 00:00:38,070
<i>Asagaya. Asagaya.</i>

9
00:00:38,980 --> 00:00:40,810
Excuse me!

10
00:00:40,810 --> 00:00:42,890
I'm getting off!

11
00:00:53,550 --> 00:00:55,840
I'm sleepy, and I don't feel rested.

12
00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:57,680
It's Saturday, but I have to go in to work,

13
00:00:57,680 --> 00:00:59,690
so it doesn't even feel like a Saturday.

14
00:00:58,220 --> 00:01:00,370
Which animal do you want to see?

15
00:01:00,370 --> 00:01:01,840
The giraffe!

16
