28
00:02:56,590 --> 00:02:57,570
Sorry.

29
00:02:57,570 --> 00:03:00,560
You looked like you were spacing out.

30
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,740
You okay?

31
00:03:03,470 --> 00:03:05,780
I think I'm a bit sleep deprived.

32
00:03:06,090 --> 00:03:08,840
