44
00:03:30,020 --> 00:03:32,560
Do Do Donuts

45
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,280
Oh.

46
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:39,860
Hifumin's the only one here?

47
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:42,760
Hifumi-senpai, good morning.

48
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:44,850
Good morning.

49
00:03:44,850 --> 00:03:46,170
Wait, what?

50
00:03:46,890 --> 00:03:48,870
Oh, these?

51
00:03:48,870 --> 00:03:52,370
I-I thought... I'd bring 
everyone some sweets.

52
00:03:57,850 --> 00:04:00,570
What do you know... We both got donuts.

53
00:04:00,570 --> 00:04:02,260
