54
00:04:02,260 --> 00:04:05,600
I think we'll just have to give 
some to the other teams, too.

55
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:09,150
Too bad Nenecchi doesn't 
work on the weekends.

56
00:04:09,150 --> 00:04:11,890
Yeah, part-timers can't work on the weekends.

57
00:04:12,130 --> 00:04:15,150
