a loophole to make wages lower?

63
00:04:28,740 --> 00:04:32,060
We can talk about that some other time.

64
00:04:34,490 --> 00:04:35,620
I know!

65
00:04:38,550 --> 00:04:41,420
I'm gonna send Nenecchi a picture of 
these donuts and make her jealous.

66
00:04:44,870 --> 00:04:46,930
You can be kind of a tease.

67
00:04:52,870 --> 00:04:55,130
Well, I'm gonna take a 
box to the design team.

68
00:04:55,130 --> 00:04:57,650
Can you take a box to Ahagon?

69
00:04:57,650 --> 00:04:58,970
Okay.

70
00:05:07,050 --> 00:05:11,740
Oh, I was just laughing because Nenecchi 
is being bitter about the donuts.

71
00:05:13,060 --> 00:05:15,080
A-Aoba-chan...

72
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:19,920
Are you the kind of person 
who's... mean to her friends?

73
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:20,730
What?

74
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:26,640
I-I don't think I... am... probably...

75
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:28,300
