76
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,790
I see...

77
00:05:31,390 --> 00:05:34,290
<i>I want to be friends with her,</i>

78
00:05:34,290 --> 00:05:40,310
<i>but if we become too close, 
she might... become mean to me.</i>

79
00:05:42,730 --> 00:05:45,730
Hifumi-senpai, you're twitching again.

80
00:05:45,730 --> 00:05:47,370
You're funny.

81
00:05:49,530 --> 00:05:52,950
Anyway, I'm going to take a box to Umiko-san.

82
00:05:52,950 --> 00:05:53,660
Oh!

83
00:05:54,430 --> 00:05:57,740
I-I'll go... too.

84
00:05:57,740 --> 00:05:59,200
Really?

85
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:00,460
Then, let's go together.

86
00:06:00,460 --> 00:06:01,860
