103
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,740
Wow, thank you!

104
00:06:44,740 --> 00:06:45,710
Yay!

105
00:06:45,710 --> 00:06:48,480
Mommy, come on! Hurry!

106
00:06:49,310 --> 00:06:51,680
