detailed reports, too.

116
00:07:35,750 --> 00:07:36,600
I see.

117
00:07:37,020 --> 00:07:39,550
So Nenecchi's working hard?

118
00:07:39,550 --> 00:07:42,230
Even the design team thinks highly of her.

119
00:07:43,520 --> 00:07:48,360
She's noted things only a hardcore fan 
would know and has been very helpful.

120
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:50,410
She's always loved games,

121
00:07:50,410 --> 00:07:53,110
and the <i>Fairies</i> series 
is one of her favorites.

122
00:07:53,420 --> 00:07:54,940
I see.

123
00:07:54,940 --> 00:07:59,620
Well, I only have a problem 
with Sakura-san's... behavior.

124
00:08:02,350 --> 00:08:05,020
I'll let her know you said that.

125
00:08:05,020 --> 00:08:06,420
Oh, anyway.

126
00:08:06,420 --> 00:08:08,140
We brought something.

127
00:08:08,140 --> 00:08:11,020
It's from Yagami-san, 
Takimoto-san, and myself.

128
00:08:11,020 --> 00:08:12,420
Thank you.

129
00:08:14,170 --> 00:08:16,450
We'll all have some later.

130
00:08:16,450 --> 00:08:18,920
Thank you, Takimoto-san.

131
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:21,630
I-It's no big...

132
00:08:21,630 --> 00:08:22,230
Huh?

133
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:25,950
Let me give you this empty 
shell as a thank you.

134
00:08:25,950 --> 00:08:27,270
You can use it as a pen holder.

135
00:08:32,350 --> 00:08:35,220
Th-Thank you.

136
00:08:35,220 --> 00:08:37,030
I'll take good care of it.

137
00:08:39,460 --> 00:08:40,320
I know.

138
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:42,360
How about we do some airsoft sometime?

139
00:08:42,970 --> 00:08:44,220
Don't worry.

140
00:08:44,220 --> 00:08:44,920
I'll back you up—

141
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:46,940
Oh! I just remembered
we have some work to do.

142
00:08:46,940 --> 00:08:48,840
We can talk about this some other time.

143
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:50,730
Hifumi-senpai, let's go!

144
00:09:00,570 --> 00:09:03,680
They can even be like matryoshka dolls.

145
00:09:07,110 --> 00:09:09,020
They should wake up soon.

146
00:09:09,800 --> 00:09:14,740
Umiko-san's a good person, but she 
can go on and on about her hobby.

147
00:09:14,740 --> 00:09:16,360
So be careful.

148
00:09:21,250 --> 00:09:22,650
I learned that the hard way.

149
00:09:22,650 --> 00:09:24,270
H-Hey.

150
00:09:25,380 --> 00:09:28,000
Thank you... for saving me.

151
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,080
Don't mention it!

152
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:31,000
It looked like you were uncomfortable.

153
00:09:31,470 --> 00:09:34,630
<i>I like it when she's nice.</i>

154
00:09:34,630 --> 00:09:38,830
But you look so cute when 
you're uncomfortable,

155
00:09:38,830 --> 00:09:41,530
so I wouldn't have minded 
watching you longer.

156
00:09:43,980 --> 00:09:46,560
Maybe I'll make you more uncomfortable.

157
00:09:48,290 --> 00:09:49,450
Just kidding.

158
00:09:50,820 --> 00:09:52,330
It was just a joke.

159
00:09:53,400 --> 00:09:57,560
<i>It didn't look like... she was joking.</i>

160
00:10:00,270 --> 00:10:02,730
Oh, good morning.

161
00:10:02,730 --> 00:10:04,240
Aoba-chan.

162
00:10:05,160 --> 00:10:07,320
Wait, why do we have more?

163
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:09,780
They were all half off.

164
00:10:09,780 --> 00:10:11,880
So we got some for all of us.

165
00:10:12,210 --> 00:10:14,880
We all had the same idea.

166
00:10:15,250 --> 00:10:16,460
Good morning.

167
00:10:16,460 --> 00:10:18,800
Thanks for coming in on a Saturday.

168
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:20,830
These are for everyone.

169
00:10:23,130 --> 00:10:25,570
It's like a donut party.

170
00:10:25,570 --> 00:10:29,440
Actually, I figured you'd get bored 
if you only had sweets, so...

171
