Salty

181
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:42,680
The infinite loop of carbs,

182
00:10:42,680 --> 00:10:46,170
and you can get a spoiled body like Mozuku.

183
00:10:47,900 --> 00:10:49,910
Um... Hazuki-san?

184
