I can't!

186
00:10:53,290 --> 00:10:55,590
There's no way I can lay a finger on these.

187
00:10:55,970 --> 00:10:58,780
This is way too much for just us here.

188
00:10:58,780 --> 00:11:01,090
We can take some to other teams.

189
00:11:01,310 --> 00:11:02,600
Yeah.

190
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:04,430
I'll take some, too.

191
00:11:04,940 --> 00:11:07,340
<i>I don't like it when she's mean.</i>

192
00:11:08,160 --> 00:11:10,440
I think I'll pass this time.

193
00:11:11,510 --> 00:11:13,250
<i>Don't look at me like that.</i>

194
00:11:17,510 --> 00:11:18,400
Sojiro.

195
00:11:18,850 --> 00:11:21,540
Sojiro, you'll be nice to me, right?

196
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,500
So cute.

197
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:34,960
Maybe I need to feed her.

198
00:11:42,070 --> 00:11:44,600
You always look so tired.

199
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:46,830
I'm fine.

200
00:11:47,460 --> 00:11:49,270
How many hours did you sleep last night?

201
00:11:50,930 --> 00:11:53,200
Maybe four hours?

202
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:56,270
I started drawing after I got 
home, so I went to bed late.

203
00:11:56,270 --> 00:11:57,890
That's not enough!

204
00:11:57,890 --> 00:12:00,300
You went to work last Saturday, too.

205
00:12:00,300 --> 00:12:01,690
You're gonna die.

206
00:12:01,690 --> 00:12:05,010
I sleep a lot on the weekends, so I'm fine.

207
00:12:05,010 --> 00:12:07,390
You've been sleeping over at work, too.

208
00:12:07,390 --> 00:12:10,340
Why do you have to work so hard?

209
00:12:10,340 --> 00:12:13,570
I think your company is weird.

210
00:12:14,760 --> 00:12:16,950
You wouldn't understand, Nenecchi.

211
00:12:16,950 --> 00:12:18,790
<i>I</i> have a dream.

212
00:12:19,940 --> 00:12:20,840
Besides...

213
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:24,220
Don't you have essays and 
homework during summer break?

214
00:12:24,220 --> 00:12:25,610
You come into work every day.

215
00:12:25,610 --> 00:12:27,450
Don't you have a life?

216
00:12:28,410 --> 00:12:30,100
You dummy!

217
00:12:31,850 --> 00:12:35,300
And Aocchi suddenly got mad at me.

218
00:12:35,910 --> 00:12:38,140
I didn't know she got mad.

219
00:12:38,140 --> 00:12:39,020
I'm surprised.

220
00:12:39,020 --> 00:12:40,450
Sympathize with me!

221
00:12:41,070 --> 00:12:43,510
Aocchi gets mad.

222
00:12:43,510 --> 00:12:45,320
Though it's pretty rare.

223
00:12:45,670 --> 00:12:46,490
