D-Don't bully Nenecchi!

242
00:13:22,650 --> 00:13:25,110
A-Aocchi...

243
00:13:25,400 --> 00:13:27,680
But she was so mean today!

244
00:13:29,420 --> 00:13:33,250
Well, I'm sure she got grumpy out of fatigue.

245
00:13:33,250 --> 00:13:35,120
You two will make up fast, I'm sure.

246
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:38,800
I-It's not like I want to make up with her.

247
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:39,880
But...

248
00:13:40,370 --> 00:13:44,760
If you finish this job with things like 
this, your friendship might actually end.

249
00:13:48,310 --> 00:13:49,720
I thought you were fine with it.

250
00:14:00,140 --> 00:14:01,360
It's already lunchtime.

251
00:14:01,710 --> 00:14:03,500
I'm hungry.

252
00:14:07,890 --> 00:14:09,250
<i>Oh, man...</i>

253
00:14:09,250 --> 00:14:12,360
<i>I got so distracted and 
couldn't get any work done.</i>

254
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:15,370
<i>Why did Nenecchi say that stuff?</i>

255
00:14:16,170 --> 00:14:18,480
Hey, what's everyone doing for lunch?

256
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:21,160
Sorry, I'm gonna grab a quick bite here.

257
00:14:21,160 --> 00:14:22,150
Same.

258
00:14:22,150 --> 00:14:23,210
Sorry.

259
00:14:23,210 --> 00:14:24,580
Okay.

260
00:14:26,050 --> 00:14:28,510
<i>Hifumi-senpai isn't here.</i>

261
00:14:29,850 --> 00:14:33,310
<i>I wonder if Nenecchi is by 
herself if I don't invite her.</i>

262
00:14:34,190 --> 00:14:35,230
<i>Whatever.</i>

263
00:14:55,140 --> 00:14:57,450
Oh, you're alone?

264
00:14:58,210 --> 00:14:59,290
Yagami-san.

265
00:14:59,290 --> 00:15:01,000
This is rare.

266
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:02,880
Are you alone, too?

267
00:15:02,880 --> 00:15:05,250
Yeah.

268
00:15:06,160 --> 00:15:08,300
Rin dumped me.

269
00:15:08,300 --> 00:15:09,760
I see.

270
00:15:09,760 --> 00:15:11,130
That was a joke!

271
00:15:15,690 --> 00:15:16,720
What's up?

272
